    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this car since day one, and it's spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
