    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, preserved in impeccable condition. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine, utilizing its sequential Hitachi twin-turbocharger system to deliver linear power delivery and a high-redline visceral experience. The chassis remains factory-spec, retaining its lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a perfectly balanced 50:50 weight distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless; the complex vacuum line network has been overhauled, and the cooling system is optimized for thermal efficiency. Power is delivered through a precise five-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. With its original paint and a pristine interior free of typical bolster wear, this FD represents the zenith of 90s analog performance engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Low mileage. No accidents. Full service history included. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
