    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six power plant. This specimen exhibits flawless mechanical synchronization, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous transient response. The dual-VANOS system has been fully serviced with upgraded seals and anti-rattle kits, and the rod bearing service is documented using VAC coated bearings and ARP hardware. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates to ensure torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential with no discernible lash. The exterior displays factory-original paint with consistent micron readings, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation or fluid seepage. Every bushing and ball joint remains within factory tolerances, preserving the legendary M-chassis kinematics. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
